com.google.api.gax.grpc

Class BundlingFuture<ResponseT>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.api.gax.grpc.BundlingFuture<ResponseT>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.google.common.util.concurrent.ListenableFuture<ResponseT>, java.util.concurrent.Future<ResponseT>

    public class BundlingFuture<ResponseT>
extends java.lang.Object
implements com.google.common.util.concurrent.ListenableFuture<ResponseT>
    A ListenableFuture to be used with bundling. It wraps a SettableFuture, and if a ThresholdBundleHandle is provided to it, it will call externalThresholdEvent to notify any BlockingCallThreshold of a blocking event (i.e. a call to get()).
